《纽约市主场迎战霍默·辛普森》于1997年9月21日通过福克斯在[[美国电视|美国]]首播。根据[[尼尔森收视率|尼尔森收视率]]调查结果，节目的收视率为10.7，相当于吸引了约1050万家庭观看，在9月15至21日这周的所有美国电视节目里排名第18。这个成绩超越《[[山丘之王|山丘之王]]》（{{lang|en|''King of the Hill''}}）第2季第1集《怎么在无需真正尝试的情况下打响步枪》（{{lang|en|''How to Fire a Rifle Without Really Trying''}}），成为福克斯该周电视节目的收视冠军。<ref>{{cite news | title = NBC lands on top; new season starts | work = Sun-Sentinel | author = Associated Press | page = 4E | date = 1997-09-25}}</ref>

节目获得评论员的普遍好评。歌曲《你正签到》获1998年[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]音乐和歌词杰出个人成就奖<ref >{{cite web | url = http://www.imdb.com/event/ev0000223/1998 | title = Awards for 1998 | work = IMDb | publisher = Amazon.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140825125525/http://www.imdb.com/event/ev0000223/1998 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-08-19 | archivedate = 2014-08-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.emmys.com/shows/simpsons | title = The Simpsons | accessdate = 2015-08-19 | publisher = Academy of Television Arts & Sciences | archivedate = 2015-06-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150708223237/http://www.emmys.com/shows/simpsons | deadurl = no}}</ref>，还获同年[[安妮奖|安妮奖]]动画电视节目杰出音乐奖<ref>{{cite news | url = http://annieawards.org/26thwinners.html | title = Legacy: 26th Annual Annie Award Nominees and Winners (1998) | accessdate = 2012-07-22 | publisher = Annie Awards | archivedate = 2012-07-22 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120722110452/http://annieawards.org/26thwinners.html}}</ref>。2003年，《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》为纪念《辛普森一家》播出300集而评选出最优秀的25集节目，《纽约市主场迎战霍默·辛普森》名列第13位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,417748_3,00.html |title=The Family Dynamic |date=2003-02-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016201945/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C417748_3%2C00.html |accessdate=2014-10-16 |publisher=Entertainment Weekly |archivedate=2014-10-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，{{lang|en|[[AskMen|AskMen]]}}网站则在评选《辛普森一家》十佳剧集时将本集排名第7<ref>{{cite web | url = http://askmen.com/toys/top_10_60/64b_top_10_list.html | title = Top 10: Simpsons Episodes | accessdate = 2015-08-19 | author = Weir, Rich | publisher = Askmen.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150510195452/http://www.askmen.com/top_10/entertainment_60/64b_top_10_list.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-05-10}}</ref>，并且在这两次评比的上榜作品中，都只有一集的播出日期比《纽约市主场迎战霍默·辛普森》更接近评选时间。{{lang|en|[[IGN|IGN]]}}将本集评为第9季最佳剧集，称“这是非常有趣的一集，以强劲音符拉开第9季的帷幕”<ref name="IGN">{{cite web | title = THE SIMPSONS: 20 SEASONS, 20 EPISODES | last1 = Goldman | first1 = Eric | author2 = Dan Iverson | author3 = Brian Zoromski | publisher = IGN | date = 2010-01-08 | accessdate = 2015-08-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150725000930/http://www.ign.com/articles/2010/01/08/the-simpsons-20-seasons-20-episodes?page=2 | url = http://uk.ign.com/articles/2010/01/08/the-simpsons-20-seasons-20-episodes?page=2 | archivedate = 2015-07-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。第9季套装{{lang|en|[[DVD|DVD]]}}发行后，多家报纸也称本集是该季最具水准的剧集<ref>{{cite news | last = Vancini | first = Daniel | title = The Simpsons – The Complete Ninth Season (1997) | work = Editorial Reviews | publisher = Amazon.com | url = http://www.amazon.com/Simpsons-Complete-Ninth-Season/dp/B000JLQPTK | accessdate = 2015-08-19 | archive-date = 2019-05-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190529154252/https://www.amazon.com/Simpsons-Complete-Ninth-Season/dp/B000JLQPTK | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Staff | title = DVDS: NEW RELEASES | work = The Mirror | page = 7 | date = 2007-02-02}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Evans | first = Mark | title = Simpsons Season 9 | work =  Evening Herald | page = 25 | date = 2007-01-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Staff | title = Present perfect; Still scrambling? Try these panic gifts with class | work = Grand Rapids Press | pages = D1 | date = 2006-12-17}}</ref>。

[[英国|英国]]评论网站“{{lang|en|Off the Telly}}”的伊恩·琼斯（{{lang|en|Ian Jones}}）和史蒂夫·威廉斯（{{lang|en|Steve Williams}}）认为，《纽约市主场迎战霍默·辛普森》的情节毫无意义，人物塑造也流于平淡，各种影像噱头和插图相互脱节，是他们眼中《辛普森一家》最糟糕的开场<ref>{{cite news | last = Williams | first = Steve | author2 = Ian Jones | title = "Now Let us Never Speak of it Again": Ian Jones and Steve Williams on the second decade of The Simpsons | work = Off the Telly | date = 2005-03 | url = http://www.offthetelly.co.uk/?page_id=373 | accessdate = 2011-11-24 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111124154146/http://www.offthetelly.co.uk/?page_id=373 | archivedate = 2011-11-24}}</ref>。两人还在网站上的另一篇文章中表示，这集节目的品味格格不入，所以永远都不会在英国地面电视台播出，意指[[英国广播公司第二台|英国广播公司第二台]]原订于2001年10月开播《辛普森一家》的计划<ref>{{cite news | last = Williams | first = Steve | author2 = Ian Jones  | title = "That is so 1991!": Steve Williams and Ian Jones on the BBC's scheduling of The Simpsons | work = Off the Telly | date = 2005-03 | url = http://www.offthetelly.co.uk/?page_id=377 | accessdate = 2011-11-24 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111124230256/http://www.offthetelly.co.uk/?page_id=377 | archivedate = 2011-11-24}}</ref>。

== 审查 ==
由于世界贸易中心在本集剧情中的重要作用，因此节目在[[九一一袭击事件|九一一袭击事件]]发生后从[[广播联卖|联卖]]中撤出<ref name="oakley" /><ref name="ofunato">{{cite news | title = 'Simpsons' exec producer Al Jean: 'I completely understand' if reruns with nuclear jokes are pulled | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2011/03/27/simpsons-al-jean-nuclear-japan | archivedate = 2015-08-19 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150819162434/http://www.ew.com/article/2011/03/27/simpsons-al-jean-nuclear-japan | work = Entertainment Weekly | accessdate = 2015-08-19 | date = 2011-03-27 | author = Snierson, Dan}}</ref>。到2006年时，部分地区已经在联卖中恢复这一集，但还是有部分内容经常被剪<ref name="weinstein" />。其中一段被剪的镜头为世贸中心双塔上两名男子的争吵，二号塔上的男子对一号塔上的男子喊道：“他们把所有的混蛋都放在一号楼上！”执行制片人比尔·欧克利表示，回想起来，这句台词“令人遗憾”<ref name="oakley" />。

